{"tid":497103,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU的大紅是天命？當年她的抓周所抓到的物品竟然是...！","createTime":"2017-12-12T11:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:03:10.000Z","uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1984a9feba0cc76bc3c426e9121023490e2ab9f8","tid":497103,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_c43b1bbc40f49fbf41d0d3c50ec64bba/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-11/100693-563332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_c43b1bbc40f49fbf41d0d3c50ec64bba%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-11%2F100693-563332.jpg&h=4f9f1867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去的週末兩天，IU舉辦了個人演唱會，除了邀請BIGBANG GD和PSY助陣擔任嘉賓以外，宋慧喬、宋仲基、李鐘碩、李準基、朴寶劍、AOA雪炫等超級明星和大勢也現身觀眾席，真正是擁有超多明星粉絲， 歌手當成這般，不得不說IU很成功！<br />\n<br />\nIU成功的秘訣到底是什麼呢？ 網路上一則「IU能夠成功的原因」的PO文引發了大眾的關注，PO主公開的照片是IU過1周歲生日時的抓周照片。 小IU身穿粉色衣服，戴著帽子，剛剛結束抓周儀式。 而她的手裡正握著剛抓取到的東西，仔細一看竟然是1萬韓幣呢~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5af29e8308af26ddf27cf907f53849eb/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-11/100693-563333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5af29e8308af26ddf27cf907f53849eb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-11%2F100693-563333.jpg&h=31172f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抓周是周歲時的預卜嬰兒前途的習俗，抓到錢幣預卜將來會賺很多錢，沒想到預卜竟然如此靈驗，現在的IU就是歌壇的小富婆啊~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_87fa8b05132ded6a832186a90b897b45/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-12-11/100693-563336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_87fa8b05132ded6a832186a90b897b45%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-12-11%2F100693-563336.jpg&h=ad8e5749&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52aae8ef14146e58095bd53c9e7e7e388cf3384c","tid":497103,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"抓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432a2f561642e211335435f8a69c0f40499ee031","tid":497103,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"張相好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fcbd426a28b29b7b0d7aa5976c495922448352","tid":497103,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6ca2488dde745ba092931268e117bb3b2cbf16","tid":497103,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張相好cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n脹卜卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cac60ee844566bb90c7f6ee13e9415cd69c5e36","tid":497103,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"佢細個真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da06adfb28694fda0038cb7a755c121b78679de6","tid":497103,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢細個真係好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile30.uf.tistory.com/original/99B9753359E8B40B31DD7E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F99B9753359E8B40B31DD7E&h=20625600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile205.uf.daum.net/original/2406DE3952D791B613EA55\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile205.uf.daum.net%2Foriginal%2F2406DE3952D791B613EA55&h=6d435f06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7c5fb